title: Chris Cagle - Play It Load (192Kbs) (2001)
description:
Play It Loud is the debut album of country music artist Chris Cagle. It features the singles "My Love Goes On and On", "Laredo", "I Breathe In, I Breathe Out", and "Country by the Grace of God"
